"aEd" = (
/obj/effect/decal/cleanable/dirt,
/obj/item/prop{
	desc = "The molten husk of an M41A Mk1 Pulse Rifle. Most of the rifle's dust cover has melted into a vauge homogenous tan painted refuge vaugely in the shape of an Mk1. The barrel has fused into the underail which in turn has fused into the ammo feed. The trigger has melted into the grip itself and the carry handle is barely recogniseable.";
